service: greeting-lambda

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs20.x
  region: us-east-1
  role: arn:aws:iam::304838291705:role/serverless-greeting-role
  environment:
    NODE_OPTIONS: "--enable-source-maps"

functions:
  greeting:
    handler: index.handler
    layers:
      - !Ref TranslateLayerLambdaLayer
  layers:
    translateLayer:
      path: layer

plugins:
  - serverless-webpack

custom:
  webpack:
    webpackConfig: ./webpack.config.js
    includeModules: true

package:
  excludeDevDependencies: true
